            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei eterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/79"
                            >Hugo</persName> gratia Dei <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Noverit
                        omnium fidelium sancte Dei Ecclesie nostrorumque presencium et futurorum
                        industria, qualiter per peticionem <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Countess #sisterOf" ref="#people/1517"
                            >Ermengardis</persName> summe <rs key="#Countess">comitisse</rs>
                        fidelissime <rs key="#sisterOf">sororis</rs> nostre <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1443"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Tower #Churches #Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">congregatio</rs> sancte <placeName
                                ref="#places/1896">Novalisiensis</placeName> ecclesie</orgName>, que
                        et nunc habitare videtur in <placeName ref="#places/8">civitate
                            Taurinensi</placeName>, pro incursione et more Paganorum, in <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1442">basilica Sancti Andree apostoli</orgName>,
                        nostre suggessit maiestati, quatenus pro Dei amore animeque nostre remedio
                        quandam <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Purchase #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1209">Bremedo</geogName> videlicet et aliam sitam
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Purchase #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1495">Policino</geogName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1444">in honore sancte Marie Dei genitricis
                            constructam</orgName>, quas curtes olim ante hos dies <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/92">Adelbertus</persName>
                        gloriosissimus <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs> per <rs key="#Cartula"
                            >cartarum instrumenta</rs> Novalisiensi cenobio <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >iure proprietario donavit</rs>, atque unam <rs key="#Tower">turrim</rs>
                        in predicta civitate constructam cum omni sua integritate et cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> sibi aderentibus, sicut ipse
                        Adelbertus eam acquisivit et eidem loco concessit, nostre a[uctorit]atis
                        pagina confirmaremus. Cuius peticionem ratam considerantes, hanc nostre
                        auctoritatis paginam scribi iussimus, per quam iam dicto cenobio prescriptas
                        duas curtes, Bremeto scilicet, quam ab <persName><name ref="Herlandus"
                                >Herlando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Inflow #Purchase">emit</rs>, et Pollicinum, quam
                        a <persName><name ref="Gisla">Gisla</name></persName> eidem Adelberto evenit
                        et iure proprietario tenuit et possedit, absque alicuius contradictione et
                        inpulsione nostra regali confirmacione roboramus et stabilimus ac perdonamus
                        ipsi cenobio Novalisiensi, pariter cum predicta turre in predicta civitate
                        constructa, sub omni integritate et cum terris sibi aderentibus, sicut idem
                        [Ade]lbertus marchio eam acquisivit et eidem loco concessit, omnino
                        transfundimus et stabilimus ad habendum, [tenendum,] et quicquid voluerit
                        secundum Deum faciendum, omnium magnarum parv[arumque] personarum
                        contradictione aut molestacione remota. Si quis vero hanc nostram
                        confirmacionem violare temptaverit, <rs key="#Penalty">mille libras
                            auri</rs> conponere cogatur, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem palacio
                            nostro</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            parti [eiusdem] Novalisiensis cenobii</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligenciusque observetur ab omnibus, manu propria roborantes ex anulo
                        nostro insigniri iussimus. Signum domni (M) Hugonis piissimi regis. Data
                        VIIII kal. Aug., anno dominice incarnacionis DCCCCXXVIIII, regni vero domni
                        Hugonis [piissimi] regis quarto, indicione secunda. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName>. Feliciter.</ab>
